{
  "stem": "210.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I used to-- she used to give me vegetables, potatoes, and tomatoes, and cucumbers, all the things that are good with the beets, to take home.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And sometimes she used to entertain the German SS, and I would be in the next room.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You know, I really didn't look that Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so I would work in the-- over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Sometimes I would do things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I would be scared to death, because I knew then in the next room there are the SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she would also be in trouble if-- if-- [LAUGHS] you know, if they would catch me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But they were really very nice, and so I worked there for awhile.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then my father went-- you know, this was, let's say, maybe six, seven months into the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "In the meantime, they did all kinds of-- they took away my uncles, you know, my mother's two-- my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "My mother's brother actually was in the-- in the Polish army, and so in '39, they drafted him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he was fighting on the Russian front, and we didn't know if he's alive or dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But my uncle was married, and he had two children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And his wife died when she gave birth to the little-- to her youngest son-- youngest boy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They had two children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So his mother-in-law took care of the children, and she lived about-- also in some kind of a store, you know, close to us and my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to take care of the children-- you know, my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because she was getting very elderly-- the-- the-- grandmother of the-- of the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my grandfather-- my uncle came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came back, you know, because he said that he could have gone into Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
